												<DIV><FONT color=#666699>I've been pretty clear about what I think should happen with Knights.</FONT></DIV>
<DIV><FONT color=#666699></FONT>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV><FONT color=#666699>&nbsp;1) Knights should get a Weaponshield type disc.</FONT></DIV>
<DIV><FONT color=#666699></FONT>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV><FONT color=#666699>&nbsp;2) Knight spellbooks need to be upgraded versus the content. This is particularly true for SK's, as they have no melee mitigation spells similar to the Paladin stun.</FONT></DIV>
<DIV><FONT color=#666699></FONT>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV><FONT color=#666699>&nbsp;3) Non plate tank classes should move to at least (DI*1.05).</FONT></DIV>
<DIV><FONT color=#666699></FONT>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV><FONT color=#666699>&nbsp;4) More raid mobs need to be 'Knight-preferred' for tanking. My personal feeling is 20-25% of an expansion's raid mobs.</FONT></DIV>
